column3: “Loved this strain and it's nice frosty look. It has a unique smell to it like a sweet/earthy OG. The nugs are really dense and break up to a nice amount but my favorite part is the high it gives a nice mental/physical relaxation. If you havent tried it i recommend you pick this 1 up and see for yourself. #🔥”

“This strain was awesome! Best strain I've tried to date.
I'm a light weight but one puff had me instantly high and feeling nice.. Fell asleep with a smile on my face after a while.”
“best GG4 hybrid with an amazing high! super fresh and sticky”
“Everyone reacts differently to each strain. This strain gave me slight paranoia, anxiety and a mild headache. I've learned I can't trust a strain that has such few reviews”
